<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>写程序的龙龙 (Posts about 我的诗词)</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/</link><description></description><atom:link href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/categories/cat_wo-de-shi-ci.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2017 17:09:08 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola (getnikola.com)</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>夜饮微醺</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ye-yin-wei-xun/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;此心憔悴不思量，望家长盼浣纱娘。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;只言片语空度日，木架犹悬嫁衣裳。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>我的诗词</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ye-yin-wei-xun/</guid><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2017 17:06:44 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>夜酌听诗</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ye-zhuo-ting-shi/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;小楼独酌诗酒茶，当年何处后庭花。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;孤星暗月空自许，秋千院落夜还家。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>我的诗词</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ye-zhuo-ting-shi/</guid><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2017 14:27:31 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>业罢伤秋</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ye-ba-shang-qiu/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;冬临万木枝灿灿，秋扫街头叶翩翩。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;枯蒿处处无颜色，干草丛丛有碧澜。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;北风易夺世间暖，艳阳难愈天下寒。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;凄凄大地行人少，朗朗乾坤一片蓝。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>我的诗词</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ye-ba-shang-qiu/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2017 15:19:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>与生共勉</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/yu-sheng-gong-mian/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;手游穷三代，追剧毁一生。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;闲聊难休止，安睡若高僧。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;时光分秒过，不与世人争。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;求学无捷径，功到自然成。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>我的诗词</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/yu-sheng-gong-mian/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 20 Jun 2017 14:42:28 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>悼别外祖母</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/dao-bie-wai-zu-mu/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;寒风送柳泛轻尘，清明未至别故人。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;心向往昔花失宠，情到痛时雨亦真。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;云中哀乐声声起，梦里忧思处处闻。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;黑纱有泪归碧海，白发无心守空门。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>我的诗词</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/dao-bie-wai-zu-mu/</guid><pubDate>Wed, 22 Mar 2017 04:12:21 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>